<L>__{exterior field early evening}
<A>__{three letters lie crumpled on the ground. toby sits with his back against a tree trunk. slowly toby opens the fourth letter. another refusal. toby tosses it onto the ground with the others, leans his head back against the tree trunk, and closes his eyes.}
